xample, increasing the SN Ia rate by\na factor of 1.8 -- to just within the 2 sigma uncertainty for present-day\ncluster early-type galaxies -- allows the combined BCG + ICS + cluster galaxy\nmodel to generate all the ICM Fe with a much lower galactic metal loss fraction\n(~ 0.35).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Oct 2008 18:44:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
